                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>For more information about partnering with AbbVie, &lt;a href=&quot;/content/dam/abbvie-com2/pdfs/partnership-approach-brochure.pdf&quot;>download our brochure&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                        </par_11>
                        <par_13
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="wcm/foundation/components/parsys">
                            <title
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-04T12:55:15.469-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-09-05T16:03:22.654-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                jcr:title="Our approach: Creating partnerships that make a difference"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                type="h2"
                                variant="h"/>
                            <text
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-04T12:56:00.281-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-04T13:13:00.695-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>At AbbVie, we partner to achieve two important outcomes: to deliver innovative medicines and to make a remarkable impact on people’s lives.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>We start with a highly integrated approach to developing and sustaining our partnerships. We work as one connected unit with a commitment to establishing collaborations across the development continuum that will ultimately benefit patients and fuel scientific progress.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Our goal is to create long-term mutually beneficial relationships. With a shared vision as our foundation, we align our collective capabilities in service of a joint mission to bring innovative medicines that solve serious health issues today and address the medical challenges of tomorrow.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>From start to finish, we ensure that everyone from working teams through senior leadership is aware of and invested in nurturing the assets we develop together. We manage for success—from early identification and mitigation of risks to shared accountability and reward for successful outcomes.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <separator
                                cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-04T13:13:17.451-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-04T13:13:17.451-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                            <title_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-04T12:55:15.469-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-09-05T16:03:32.871-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                jcr:title="How we work together"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                type="h2"
                                variant="h"/>
                            <text_259153141
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-17T14:03:15.858-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-06-02T11:24:21.219-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>&lt;b>Search and Evaluation&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>We focus on identifying and evaluating new opportunities that complement and enhance&amp;nbsp; our existing internal innovation strategies. S&amp;amp;E works in close partnership with our R&amp;amp;D&amp;nbsp; and commercial teams, BD&amp;amp;A and Ventures&amp;nbsp; to thoughtfully address each opportunity.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Business Development and Acquisitions&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>We evaluate a variety of partnership structures to meet the needs of both parties. BD&amp;amp;A works closely with S&amp;amp;E,&amp;nbsp; and our commercial and R&amp;amp;D organizations&amp;nbsp; to evaluate new opportunities.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Global Alliances&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>Highly successful partnerships result from an ongoing commitment to realize a shared vision. At AbbVie, we have a dedicated team that is involved in all aspects of the partnership from contracting through commercialization.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>AbbVie Ventures&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>We strategically invest in transformational scientific opportunities to augment our core R&amp;amp;D interests and gain access to next-generation science and proven scientific leaders. Our expertise in drug development and commercialization can be a valuable resource to even the earliest stage companies.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <separator_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-04T13:13:17.451-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-04T13:13:17.451-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                            <separator_copy_1916185142
